tvOS isn&rsquo;t getting the credit it deserves. I've found Apple TV the platform that I&rsquo;ve had the most fun developing for in a long time.
The television is the physically largest canvas currently available. What has been a central point of the living room has historically been the most difficult thing to break into. The number of people willing to build awkwardly horrible &ldquo;Samsung apps&rdquo;, for example, are very few.

