Write a letter of love to yourself to read again in one year. And then some stuff that has to do with getting away from the computer.
If you haven't noticed, I'm going to ignore the parts of this project that deals with getting away from the computer and doing things. That's not really my jam. Journal, stamps, special pens, beautiful paper, stickers, glue, etc... not things I own.

